==Bio==

"James serves internationally providing organizational development consultancy, learning facilitation and mentoring for people wishing to increase business agility and grow agile and responsive learning organizations where people and company thrive. 

He combines extensive experience of sociocracy with 15 years practice in the fields of holistic organizational development, facilitative leadership and personal and relational transformation. He currently spends most of his time supporting others to learn about [[Sociocracy 3.0]] and working directly with organizations to help them improve productivity and raise engagement, whatever their size."<br />
